[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "ええと、ホロッとした食感にするには……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ルアッカ",
		"romanized_name": "RUAKKA",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おい。そこの素材じゃねぇか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "あ、ありがとう、ルアッカ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "クリセルダ……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（初めは、クリセルダがパルメ族の存在に\n　気付いたこと）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（私たちの歴史に自由なんかないことに気付いて、\n　解放を目指して極夜の錬金党を立ち上げて）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（そんなクリセルダの元に、渇望を持つ仲間が\n　集ってきた）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（私も、クリセルダに救われて仲間になって、\n　それ以来、ずっと一緒にいる）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "ふふ。それから、どんなことがあっても幸せだった",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（私たちは、渇望のためなら他の人のことなんか\n　顧みず、世間では悪事と呼ばれることもした）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（それでも信念があった）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（その信念のために戦い抜いて、レスナたちに敗れて、\n　そして、今があって）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "幸せ、だなぁ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "アオナ",
		"romanized_name": "AONA",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "故郷では、誰にも認められずに「魔女」だなんて\n呼ばれてたんだもんね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ムラサキ",
		"romanized_name": "MURASAKI",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "アンチュ君が、極夜の錬金党に入ったことを、\nとんでもない回り道なんて言う人はいるだろうけれど",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "うん。そんなことはまったくない",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "クリセルダと出会えなかったら。\n錬金党じゃなかったら……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "私は、私の渇望を閉じ込めてしまって、\n今の私じゃなかったから",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（改めてクリセルダに「ありがとう」って\n　伝えたいの）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]